descriptor.name: Sales Executive
descriptor.long_desc:
- Prospect and generate new sales opportunities through networking, cold calling, and social media
- Build and maintain relationships with potential and existing clients to drive sales growth
- Meet or exceed sales targets by effectively selling the company's products or services
- Provide exceptional customer service and support to clients throughout the sales process
- Conduct product demonstrations and presentations to showcase the features and benefits of the company's offerings
- Stay up-to-date on industry trends and competitors to identify new business opportunities
- Collaborate with the marketing team to develop promotional materials and campaigns to support sales efforts
- Prepare and submit sales reports and forecasts to management on a regular basis

Requirements:

- Proven track record of success in sales, with 2-3 years of experience in a similar role
- Strong communication and interpersonal skills to build rapport with clients and colleagues
- Ability to work independently and as part of a team in a fast-paced environment
- Knowledge of sales techniques and strategies to close deals and achieve sales goals
- Familiarity with the BANGALORE market and industry trends to effectively identify sales opportunities
- Bachelor's degree in business, marketing, or related field preferred
- Willingness to travel within BANGALORE for client meetings and sales presentations.
